S.FORM: O Pakeriran (Holam: 巴克力藍的夏天) cacey kamoko'ay a tilifi ega i Taywan. Misanga' Pipahosoan to tilifi no Yen-cu-min ci ina to tilifi ega. Mipasadak to 2017 a miheca. Mianingaya a patingso^ Matam Hidaw
